(all 99%)<br>
Ungrouped (no druid melee speed buff), or grouped with a good nurture druid:<br>
Arcanite bastard sword<br>
Arcanite sickle<br>
<br>
Grouped (no melee buff, or very little)<br>
2 Arcanite sickles<br>
<br>
